component_text: people normally have lots of things to do
they don’t have much time to spend in the kitchen
being able to prepare a tasty food just putting it into the microwave or into the oven is awesome
if an engineer needs to make a project, but he needs to deliver it tomorrow, he could save hours preparing a food with the microwave instead of cooking everything from scratch

when someone wants to prepare a good food alone for some reason, some time ago he/she would need to be a very good cook to prepare that food, but nowadays is very easy to prepare a healthy and tasty food
if a guy wants to prepare a dinner to his girlfriend, he could just buy some food that comes with instructions
Normally you just need to put it into the oven and wait some time
ease to prepare food has improved people’s lives
But people should be careful with what they eat
some industrial foods are very bad for their health
they should buy only food from well known brands
